### 1️⃣ 먼저 이 요청을 실행해서 토큰을 받으세요
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

> {%
client.global.set("authToken", response.body.token);
%}

###

### 2️⃣ 모든 제품 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 3️⃣ 제품 생성 (판매용)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "캠핑 텐트",
  "stockQuantity": 10,
  "price": 150000,
  "productType": "SALE"
}

###

### 4️⃣ 제품 생성 (렌탈용)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "캠핑 의자",
  "stockQuantity": 20,
  "price": 5000,
  "productType": "RENTAL"
}

###

### 5️⃣ 제품 수정 (제품 ID를 실제 값으로 변경하세요)
PUT http://localhost:8080/admin/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "수정된 제품명",
  "stockQuantity": 15,
  "price": 200000,
  "productType": "SALE"
}